@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rwjpaq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.cos((v1 + 0.78 - v1 + 0.08)) - 0.04)
    v0 = ((wp.cos(v2 + 0.30) + wp.sin(tmp + 0.80)) + ((tmp + 0.27 + v2 + 0.29) - v2))
    v2 = tmp
    v2 = ((v2 - wp.abs(v0 + 0.57)) * 0.25)
    tmp = (wp.abs(v0) * wp.exp(wp.sin(tmp + 0.14)))
    v2 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
